00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:07.559
Si no, seremos cuatro,

00:07:07.959 --> 00:07:08.880
seremos uno.

00:07:25.240 --> 00:07:27.768
(Monte Yuqing,)

00:07:42.040 --> 00:07:44.320
Jin Zhao, no quiero perder...

00:07:45.519 --> 00:07:46.519
No quiero perder...

